    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-8079-be6f-c0c9450d900a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Using learner logs to create early-warning systems is, while useful conceptually, highly dependent on knowledge-domain (because different disciplines tend to require different forms of engagement which, in turn, often leads to differences in interaction patterns).  ",
